{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/etc/2024-07-15-logical clock (lamport clock)/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1>logical clock</h1>\n<p>컴퓨터세계에서 로컬 timestamp는 썩 믿을만한 것이 못됩니다.</p>\n<p>보통 대부분의 PC는 NTP라는 프로토콜을 이용해 시간을 동기화하고 사용하는데, 이는 네트워크를 이용해 시간을 동기화하는 것이므로 네트워크가 불안정하거나 끊겨있다면 실제 시간과 오차값이 커질 수도 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c0b5072945f0680310ddf94dec334bb0/683d4/Untitled.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.47916666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/c0b5072945f0680310ddf94dec334bb0/a59e9/Untitled.webp 192w,\n/static/c0b5072945f0680310ddf94dec334bb0/0ca9f/Untitled.webp 384w,\n/static/c0b5072945f0680310ddf94dec334bb0/dc9b9/Untitled.webp 768w,\n/static/c0b5072945f0680310ddf94dec334bb0/e2c2f/Untitled.webp 1152w,\n/static/c0b5072945f0680310ddf94dec334bb0/6ba46/Untitled.webp 1174w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/c0b5072945f0680310ddf94dec334bb0/3b721/Untitled.png 192w,\n/static/c0b5072945f0680310ddf94dec334bb0/66595/Untitled.png 384w,\n/static/c0b5072945f0680310ddf94dec334bb0/fe486/Untitled.png 768w,\n/static/c0b5072945f0680310ddf94dec334bb0/d2d74/Untitled.png 1152w,\n/static/c0b5072945f0680310ddf94dec334bb0/683d4/Untitled.png 1174w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/c0b5072945f0680310ddf94dec334bb0/fe486/Untitled.png\"\n            alt=\"Untitled\"\n            title=\"Untitled\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>때문에 분산 컴퓨팅에서 로컬의 timestamp를 믿고 개발을 진행하는 건 상당히 위험한데, 그래서 나온 것이 <strong>Logical Clock</strong>이라는 것입니다.</p>\n<p>Logical Clock이 중요하게 생각하는 것은 각 이벤트가 “언제 발생했느냐”보단 <strong>“A가 B보다 먼저 발생했느냐”</strong> 를 중요하게 여깁니다.</p>\n<p>즉 인과관계를 중요하게 여기는 것입니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/3f970/Untitled1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.95833333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/a59e9/Untitled1.webp 192w,\n/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/0ca9f/Untitled1.webp 384w,\n/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/dc9b9/Untitled1.webp 768w,\n/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/e2c2f/Untitled1.webp 1152w,\n/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/f3efb/Untitled1.webp 1536w,\n/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/74615/Untitled1.webp 1806w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/3b721/Untitled1.png 192w,\n/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/66595/Untitled1.png 384w,\n/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/fe486/Untitled1.png 768w,\n/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/d2d74/Untitled1.png 1152w,\n/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/e8464/Untitled1.png 1536w,\n/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/3f970/Untitled1.png 1806w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/c607d52072dc805fad7244e9ed85c730/fe486/Untitled1.png\"\n            alt=\"Untitled\"\n            title=\"Untitled\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>그래서 위의 경우 a, b, c, d, f 끼리는 인과관계가 명확하게 주어지지만, a, b, c, d와 e 사이에는 무엇이 먼저인지 나중인지 알 수 없습니다.</p>\n<h2>Lamport clocks</h2>\n<p>램포트라는 사람이 1978년에 발표한 알고리즘입니다.</p>\n<p>이벤트간에 Partial ordering을 제공하고, 이벤트마다 Logical clock을 붙여줍니다.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"python\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\"># 이벤트가 알려지면</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">time = time + </span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;        </span><span class=\"mtk3\"># receiving</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">                        (message, time_stamp) = receive()</span><span class=\"mtk14\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">                        time = </span><span class=\"mtk11\">max</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(time_stamp, time) + </span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk14\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\"># 이벤트 발생시</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">send(message, time)</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Lamport Clock은 항상 아래를 만족합니다.</p>\n<p>이벤트 a와 b가 인과관계에 있을 때 a의 Logical Clock &#x3C;  b의 Logical Clock 입니다.</p>\n<p>$$\nif \\ a → b \\\nthen \\ C(a) &#x3C; C(b)\n$$</p>\n<h3>인과관계</h3>\n<p>인과관계에 있는 이벤트간에는 반드시 logical Time으로 대소비교가 가능합니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/89060/Untitled2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.541666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/a59e9/Untitled2.webp 192w,\n/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/0ca9f/Untitled2.webp 384w,\n/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/dc9b9/Untitled2.webp 768w,\n/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/e2c2f/Untitled2.webp 1152w,\n/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/f3efb/Untitled2.webp 1536w,\n/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/b0015/Untitled2.webp 2808w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/3b721/Untitled2.png 192w,\n/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/66595/Untitled2.png 384w,\n/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/fe486/Untitled2.png 768w,\n/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/d2d74/Untitled2.png 1152w,\n/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/e8464/Untitled2.png 1536w,\n/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/89060/Untitled2.png 2808w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d233c9a5a0bf2e05ebab6a0ad9f132fe/fe486/Untitled2.png\"\n            alt=\"Untitled\"\n            title=\"Untitled\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>동시 이벤트</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/71071/Untitled3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.0625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/a59e9/Untitled3.webp 192w,\n/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/0ca9f/Untitled3.webp 384w,\n/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/dc9b9/Untitled3.webp 768w,\n/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/e2c2f/Untitled3.webp 1152w,\n/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/f3efb/Untitled3.webp 1536w,\n/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/48092/Untitled3.webp 2802w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/3b721/Untitled3.png 192w,\n/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/66595/Untitled3.png 384w,\n/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/fe486/Untitled3.png 768w,\n/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/d2d74/Untitled3.png 1152w,\n/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/e8464/Untitled3.png 1536w,\n/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/71071/Untitled3.png 2802w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a8239395d648765b7605f05a561f1422/fe486/Untitled3.png\"\n            alt=\"Untitled\"\n            title=\"Untitled\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>한계</h3>\n<p>하지만 Lamport Clock은 아래는 보장하지 못합니다.</p>\n<p>$$\nif \\ C(a) &#x3C; C(b) \\\nthen \\ a → b\n$$</p>\n<h3>쓰이는 예시</h3>\n<p><strong>4. 분산 로그 및 이벤트 추적 시스템</strong></p>\n<p>Lamport Clock은 로그와 이벤트의 순서를 결정하는 데 유용합니다.</p>\n<p><strong>예시</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>여러 서버에서 발생하는 로그를 중앙집중식으로 수집하고 분석합니다.</li>\n<li>각 서버는 로그를 생성할 때 자신의 Lamport Clock 값을 포함시킵니다.</li>\n<li>중앙 로그 수집 시스템은 로그를 수집할 때, Lamport Clock 값을 기준으로 로그의 순서를 정렬합니다.</li>\n<li>이를 통해 시스템 전체의 이벤트 순서를 일관되게 유지할 수 있습니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 366px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/44eb3f24ab640aa3fe9ed63bcfe37a78/b18e8/Untitled4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 37.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/44eb3f24ab640aa3fe9ed63bcfe37a78/a59e9/Untitled4.webp 192w,\n/static/44eb3f24ab640aa3fe9ed63bcfe37a78/fe2f8/Untitled4.webp 366w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 366px) 100vw, 366px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/44eb3f24ab640aa3fe9ed63bcfe37a78/3b721/Untitled4.png 192w,\n/static/44eb3f24ab640aa3fe9ed63bcfe37a78/b18e8/Untitled4.png 366w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 366px) 100vw, 366px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/44eb3f24ab640aa3fe9ed63bcfe37a78/b18e8/Untitled4.png\"\n            alt=\"Untitled\"\n            title=\"Untitled\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>예를 들어 위와 같이 로그가 쌓였다고 했을 때,</p>\n<p>a와 h는 순서와 상관없이 섞여서 쌓이겠지만, h, b, c, e, j는 정확하게 순서대로 쌓일 수 있습니다.. (중간 중간 다른 것들은 순서가 섞여 있겠지만)</p>\n<h2>참고</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OKHIdpOAxto\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OKHIdpOAxto</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x-D8iFU1d-o\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x-D8iFU1d-o</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1wceo1cDpWtZr2Q-GJ8VuZDhQYTkciFKS/view\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1wceo1cDpWtZr2Q-GJ8VuZDhQYTkciFKS/view</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://m.blog.naver.com/stallon72/10030817453\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://m.blog.naver.com/stallon72/10030817453</a></p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-paddi